comment.body:
>anarcho-capitalist telling people what to do.



That's not very anarcho of you.
I'd agree with the restriction, actually. This is content *no one* should be viewing, let alone children who are susceptible to misinformation.

You're posting a message about free speech on the internet by posting to a forum that's *more* free than gab. Lmao. Yeah I'll stick to ZeroMe and ZeroVoat, thanks. ICANN didn't 'ban you'. If they really wanted your shit off the internet, they'd ban gab as well. The only way ICANN would give a shit is if you were a large site hosting illegal content (copyrighted stuff and CP). At which point gab won't save you.
